 (29051009), <a href="/web/20180712194719/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0354100&amp;fLockTerm=Loop+diuretic">Loop diuretic</a>
 (372691009), <a href="/web/20180712194719/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0278314&amp;fLockTerm=Nephrostomy">Nephrostomy</a>
 (39834009), <a href="/web/20180712194719/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0028961&amp;fLockTerm=Oliguria">Oliguria</a>
